summary: A game conversion, more fighting, more npcs, more loot. PM me if you wanna help and what u can do.
descriptionHtml: A big mod, no idea when it will be done, but we are changing the Empire to Sith and the Emperor will be Darth Revan, the Stormcloaks will be Jedi and Ulfric will be Yoda and more. We will have children be either sith/jedi that attack depending where they are in the world and even Sith/Jedi followers. Everyone who contributed will have their own npc in the game and can get quests from. More to come
author: The SSVJM Team
